name: Httpebble-simple
tagline: This is a lightweight httpebble application for pebble watches. It isn't a watchface, but it still waits in the background for any httpebble requests.
body:
light-httpebble
===============

This is a lightweight httpebble application for pebble watches.
It isn't a watchface, but it still waits in the background for any httpebble requests.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
